room_title: Escape room "The Pirate's Chamber" by Captured LV Escape Room in Bethlehem
room_description: Captain Bruce Bowing and his crew of pirates have stolen a treasure from the Island of Magu. You have found Captain Bruce’s ship and have gone aboard, but you were captured and are now being held prisoner. You need to retrieve the treasure from Captain Bruce’s room and escape his chambers before they notice you went missing!
